HEADWORD: noncommital
<hw>noncommital</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Not expressing a preference;
<as>as, although favoring European unity he was <ex>noncommittal</ex>
about the form it should take</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> undogmatic.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

